igbFinisher has been updated to version 3.1.0 with the following updates:
[list]
[li]Added support for AnimationProducer, which allows for skins to be built into default-style animation databases, removing the dummy animation and slightly reducing file size.[/li]
[li]Added some additional hex editing to skins to more closely match default skin structure.[/li]
[li]Improved handling of environment maps to address some detection issues.[/li]
[/list]